metadata.name: Born at Night
metadata.description:
The artwork you see is different than the artwork your friends see.

Turn the brightness at various levels so you could really see the magic.

Now think about how much cooler it would be if that art was different every time you see it.

You know, just to keep things fresh and interesting.

1/1 collections (Only 10 in existence)

And the effects of the artwork varies on your gadgets you used.
